
           =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=- Half Orc -=-=-=-=-=-=

    Half-Orcs have a human appearance.  They are too slow-witted
for anything other than common fighting.


SUMMARY:

Dex: Avg           Str: High            Con: High
Int: Below Ag      Wis: Below Avg       Char: Below Avg

Sight: Avg
HP Regen: Nil
SP Regen: Nil
Natural Weaponry: Standard (Above Avg)
Natural Armour: Nil
Ambidextry: Nil 
Innate spells/skills: Nil
Exp Modifier: High

